    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>Penn Automotive has been a fixture of the Pittsburgh area for over 65 years. What started as a family business in West Homestead has grown into one of the most trusted collision repair shops in southwestern Pennsylvania — without ever losing the personal touch that makes us different.</p>

    <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
    <p>Owner Joel Feldman is the only mechanical engineer in Pittsburgh to run his own collision shop. As a licensed damage appraiser and mechanic with over 30 years of hands-on experience, Joel brings a level of technical depth that most body shops simply can't match.</p>
    <p>We invest in staff training and modern diagnostic equipment so we can properly service today's vehicles — not just the ones from 30 years ago.</p>

    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Lifetime written guarantee on all restoration work</li>
      <li>Transparent communication throughout every repair</li>
      <li>Customer car loan program available</li>
      <li>Conveniently located on a major roadway in West Homestead</li>
    </ul>

